{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0bec697888","title":"中共中央、国务院关于今年小学放暑假的通知","origin":"根据中共中央办公厅、国务院秘书厅文化革命联合接待室编印《无产阶级文化大革命有关文件汇集 （第三集）》， 北京：1967年9月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"215a83a870","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":17,"articleId":"0bec697888"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3fa4110965","type":"title","text":"中共中央、国务院关于今年小学放暑假的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0bec697888"},{"id":"0009f70002","type":"appellation","text":"各省、市、自治区革命委员会（筹备小组）、军事管制委员会、各军区、各省军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0bec697888"},{"id":"44c25bfcac","type":"paragraph","text":"一、中央决定今年小学可以在八月份放暑假，十月开学。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0bec697888"},{"id":"c09e9d9318","type":"paragraph","text":"二、暑假期间，各校要很好地整顿教师的思想，组织教师参加大批判运动；并整修校舍，积极准备迎接新学年。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0bec697888"}],"page":{"id":"1d6cd20dca","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0bec697888","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}